title: 7/4 Wrestling Observer Radio: WWE Beast In The East, NJPW Domini
description:
Saturday, 04 July 2015 13:48 


Wrestling Observer Radio with Dave Meltzer and Mike Sempervive returns on AMERICA'S INDEPENDENCE DAY with a wrap-up of this morning's WWE Beast In The East live network special from Tokyo's Sumo Hall. Few surprises, but two great matches - including Finn Balor upending Kevin Owens for the NXT championship. We also have an impromptu mini-history of wrestling in Hawaii, the Wednesday night ratings fall-out (which fell-out), a big departure for TNA, Tough Enough, Smackdown on USA, tomorrow morning's New Japan Dominion show lineup, a special announcement about tomorrow's show and much more. A fun show as always, so check it out!
